title: Ebro In The Morning - A Gaggle of Goofies + The Temperature Wars
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/13/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are back in the studio - Ebro is not amused by the gaggle of goofies, the crew discusses the television shows they're watching, and a heated debate about heat is had. Find out who played themselves!
